Senior Oracle Supply Chain Management
30 Apr 2014 02:44 PM - UAE
Senior Oracle Supply Chain Management Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirate Oracle Supply Chain Management / SCM Oracle Supply Chain Management / SCM One of the leading vendors in the world currently has an urgent requirement for a Oracle SCM (Supply Chain Management) to work in Abu Dhabi, I am Looking for a strong purchasing, Inventory / Order management professional. The successful candidate will need to have a minimum 10 years experience, should have worked with at least 4-5 Supply Chain management implementations and should know the SCM activities interfacing with finance module. If you feel you are a good fit for the above requirements and would like further information or if the position is not right for you but you know someone that you think could be good for the role please contact me as soon as possible - faressalman@pentaconsulting.com or call me on 0208 254 7480 Penta Consulting is a global staffing solutions business providing innovative and flexible recruitment strategies for clients and the very best permanent, interim and contract career opportunities for candidates across IT & Telecoms. Ranked 8 in the 2013 Sunday Times Top 100 Companies to Work For awards, Penta holds a Queen's Award for (more...)
